      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "from the wrath to come",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "] The Jews had been taught by Prophecy that the Advent of their Deliverer should be preceded by a time of anguish which they called “the Woes of the Messiah;” comp. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
