        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", “Who may abide the day of His coming? and who shall stand when He appeareth? For He is like a refiner’s fire, and like fuller’s soap.” ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
